            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The skullcrushers fling a fusillade of sling bullets enchanted with life energy intended to destroy undead. This barrage is a 10-foot burst within 50 feet that deals 3d6 bludgeoning damage plus 1d6 vitality damage to undead, with a DC 22 basic Reflex save. When the troop is reduced to 2 or fewer segments, this area decreases to a 5-foot burst.",
            "traits": [
